---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer - MindLooker">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Important Disclaimer</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      
      <div class="bg-brand-accent/20 border-l-4 border-brand-accent p-6 mb-8">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">READ THIS CAREFULLY</p>
        <p>
          MindLooker is NOT therapy, counseling, or medical treatment. It is a structured process 
          for self-examination. If you need medical or mental health care, seek appropriate 
          professional help immediately.
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Not Medical or Mental Health Services</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          <strong>MindLooker sessions and practitioner training are NOT:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Medical, psychiatric, or psychological treatment</li>
          <li>Therapy, counseling, or coaching</li>
          <li>A diagnosis or treatment for any condition</li>
          <li>A substitute for professional medical or mental health care</li>
          <li>Emergency or crisis intervention services</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-4">
          MindLooker practitioners are not therapists, counselors, or medical professionals 
          (unless separately licensed, which is independent of their MindLooker training).
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">No Guarantees</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We make no promises about outcomes. MindLooker provides a process, not results. 
          What you discover and what you do with those discoveries is entirely up to you.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Individual experiences vary greatly. Past participant results don't predict your experience.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Your Responsibility</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          By participating in MindLooker sessions or training, you acknowledge that:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>You are fully responsible for your own decisions and actions</li>
          <li>You will not rely on MindLooker as medical or mental health treatment</li>
          <li>You will seek appropriate professional help when needed</li>
          <li>You participate at your own risk</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Emergency Situations</h2>
        <div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-500 p-6 mb-4">
          <p class="font-semibold mb-2">If you are experiencing a medical or mental health emergency:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Call 911 (or your local emergency number) immediately</li>
            <li>Go to your nearest emergency room</li>
            <li>Contact the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline: 988</li>
            <li>Contact the Crisis Text Line: Text HOME to 741741</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p class="mb-4">
          MindLooker is not equipped to handle emergencies and should never be used as 
          crisis intervention.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Information Accuracy</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          While we strive for accuracy, information on this website is provided "as is" without 
          warranty. We don't guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or usefulness of any information.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Blog posts, testimonials, and other content represent individual opinions and experiences, 
          not medical or professional advice.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Financial Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Any earnings or income statements are estimates only. Your results depend entirely on 
          your own efforts, skills, and circumstances. We make no guarantees about your ability 
          to earn income as a MindLooker practitioner.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Links to Other Sites</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Our website may contain links to third-party sites. We're not responsible for their 
          content, privacy practices, or any damages from your use of those sites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, MindLooker, its owners, employees, practitioners, 
          and affiliates will not be liable for any damages arising from:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
          <li>Your use or inability to use our services</li>
          <li>Any decisions or actions you take based on our services</li>
          <li>Any errors or omissions in our content</li>
          <li>Personal injury or emotional distress</li>
          <li>Lost profits or other consequential damages</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Indemnification</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          You agree to defend, indemnify, and hold harmless MindLooker and its associates from 
          all claims, damages, and expenses arising from your use of our services or violation 
          of this disclaimer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Severability</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          If any part of this disclaimer is found to be unenforceable, the remaining portions 
          will continue in full force and effect.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Questions about this disclaimer? Contact us at:
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Email: legal@mindlooker.com<br>
          Website: www.mindlooker.com
        </p>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-lg">
        <p class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">By using this website or our services, you acknowledge:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>You have read and understood this disclaimer</li>
          <li>You agree to all its terms</li>
          <li>You are participating at your own risk</li>
          <li>You will seek appropriate professional help when needed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
